Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:06.25,Black Title,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1752,6256}{\blur0.75\fs150\pos(906,346)}Michiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:7424,9843}Togashi-kun, don't forget us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:9843,11345}Take care of yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:11345,12346}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:12346,13388}You too, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:13388,14514}Do your best over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:14514,17059}Thank you, I'll write to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:17059,18602}I'll write too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:18602,20646}Come by now and then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:20938,23732}Don't go finding yourself\Na girlfriend, Togashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:28612,34701}{\i1}And just like that, the person I loved\Nwas transferring schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:35911,40999}{\i1}I wish we made more memories.\NWe didn't talk much all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44711,45629}I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:46129,47923}Ah, Michiyo, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:47923,50008}Look, your aunt is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50008,51552}Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:51927,55514}Oh, my, Micchan.\NYou look as lively as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:55514,58267}What were you doing,\Nagain? Basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:58267,60477}Oh, no, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:60477,63188}Oh, no, dear,\Nher skin is always dark like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63188,67651}But she's so tall. What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:67651,72823}Don't let the appearances fool you.\NHer reflexes are worse than useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:72823,75200}I wonder who she got that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75200,77953}Masako, you can't say\Nthings like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:77953,79079}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79079,82124}That's just how I am.\NA dark, plain old bean pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82416,84084}See, she got mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84084,88130}It's fine,\Nshe'll get over it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89006,92551}So, how did Togashi-san's\Ngoodbye party go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92551,96096}Akiko and Youko started to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97180,98265}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:98265,99516}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99516,103812}Why? You always really liked\NTogashi-san, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106440,109484}I didn't hear that,\Nwhy don't you say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109484,113572}That hurts!\NI'm sorry, just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113572,114656}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115407,117159}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:02:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117159,120871}It's it cute?\NAuntie handed it down to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120871,122247}Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122247,126251}Well… it would be\Ntoo short for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126251,129421}It wouldn't suit me,\Nanyway, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129421,131798}It's a shame you're that tall, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131798,132716}Chinatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132716,133425}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137804,141808}{\i1}I wish I was cuter\Nand more ladylike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141808,144644}{\i1}If I was, I'd be able to\Nget on better with Togashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147606,151485}{\i1}I'm sure he'll forget all about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160285,161995}{\i1}My head hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164581,167209}Your fever isn't going down at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167209,168668}You'll have to stay in bed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168668,170504}I'll speak to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170504,173423}She must've been really shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173423,173965}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173965,174758}Chinatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174758,177552}Ah, it's nothing, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177552,180305}Well, you should try\Nand get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182849,186144}What? The boy she likes\Nhas transferred schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186144,189439}Oh, my! I didn't think\Nshe had someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189439,191358}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191358,195570}But if she wanted him to notice her,\Nshe should've been more ladylike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199491,204538}{\i1}What? It's always you\Nwho buys me boyish clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204538,206415}{\i1}It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207916,210877}Michiyo, we're going shopping,\Nso stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224224,227436}Oh, that's right.\NNobody's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232190,233442}A delivery?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234443,236486}I have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236486,238447}Oh, the stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242784,245370}They were just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.41,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:247956,249416}From Togashi\Nto Kakimoto Michiyo-san
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249791,251877}What?! It's from Togashi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260343,261052}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266057,268643}"How are you, Kakimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268643,272772}I'm sure you'll be surprised that\Nthis turned up out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272772,276109}I've moved in with my grandma\Nin the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.10,0:04:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276109,281490}but my grandma is ill, and before she passes,\Nshe wants to see the girl I'll marry."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283533,290123}"It's too soon for me to get married and\NI keep telling her that, but she doesn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290123,292209}She'd also like to give you a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292209,295504}This one piece is very special to her,\Nand she'd love to see you wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295504,297422}Sorry that it's on\Nsuch a short notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297422,302219}but can you wear it this Sunday and meet me\Nat the Usakuracho bus station at 2 p.m.?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302219,303970}This Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304763,306389}That's tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306389,308391}"You're the only person\NI can ask this."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316441,319319}{\i1}I can't believe it. It suits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325283,326952}{\i1}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332332,335919}You barely got sick\Nand you're already healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335919,337671}It's because I'm young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337671,340757}Are you sure that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340757,342050}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342050,346680}So, we can all go\Nshopping tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346680,349182}Actually, I've made\Na promise with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349182,351017}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351017,352435}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352435,353937}Sounds fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353937,354729}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354729,356022}Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356022,357023}See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357023,358650}Bring me something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362279,363363}Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368994,372038}That's right.\NI could be late getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373039,374499}I'll write Chinatsu a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:17.46,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:374499,377460}{\an2}Chinatsu, I've actually gone\Nto see Togashi-kun. – Michiyo {\pbo10\p1}m 0 0 b 0 -12.25 18 -12.25 21 3 b 24 -12.25 42 -12.25 42 0 b 42 14 21 24.5 21 24.5 b 21 24.5 0 14 0 0 c{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389472,390765}Kakimoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391266,392225}Togashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409409,410952}She still isn't back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410952,413955}She's late.\NIt's already dark, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413955,417042}I'll try phoning one of her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417042,418752}Yes, if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419044,422380}Let's see…\NHer address book…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425926,429179}What? What's this…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429971,431473}What is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431473,434601}She's going to get told off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436102,440231}Oh, hello, Akiko-san?\NThis is Kakimoto Michiyo's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440231,443568}Do you have Togashi-san's\Nphone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443568,446237}{\i1}Huh? Togashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446237,450492}{\i1}Oh, that's right. Kakimoto was off\Nyesterday, so she wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450492,457165}{\i1}He was really unlucky. He was caught up\Nin a terrible crash when he was moving house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459376,462045}{\i1}He died,\Nalong with the entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463797,469594}{\i1}Hello? Kakimoto-san, are you there?\NWas it something about Togashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469594,472931}{\i1}Hello? Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474140,477477}{\i1}That was when I knew\Nshe wasn't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478812,481022}{\i1}The police have been\Nsearching for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481022,484943}{\i1}they've even made the public know,\Nbut they haven't gotten any leads yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485443,487904}{\i1}But there was one story I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487904,492867}{\i1}There was a pretty girl wearing\Na one piece around Usakuracho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492867,497956}{\i1}She was holding hands with\Na scruffy looking man, and having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497956,501501}{\i1}But those are just rumors.\NI know they aren't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501501,503920}{\i1}She'll come back, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509968,511553}Coming!
